TV




Parameters: \(m\), \(n\), \(\xi\), \(\lambda\), \(\Omega\) \[\begin{equation*}
n=\frac{S}{S + U} \text{ , } m=\frac{T}{T + V}
\end{equation*}\] \[\begin{equation*}
\xi=\frac{T + V}{S + U}
\end{equation*}\] \[\begin{equation*}
\Omega=\frac{S + T}{S + T + U + V}=\frac{m + n \xi}{\xi + 1}
\end{equation*}\] \[\begin{equation*}
\lambda=\frac{S + V}{S + T + U + V}=\frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma + 1}
\end{equation*}\]
